{"tid":1175204,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"外置硬碟壞咗，求救!","createTime":"2019-05-28T11:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T23:56:35.000Z","uid":133689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"efe5ab7d4c1213085dcb933c9197c2394a1a0a1a","tid":1175204,"uid":133689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"我買左這個外置硬碟多年，最近佢detect 唔到，硬碟有哂重要既相和檔，所以係連登向各位求救!<br />\n<br />\nWD software 顯示我個harddisk 有電到，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3wAXFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3wAXFe.jpg&h=701f532a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但咩都睇唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfsXryy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfsXryy.jpg&h=829e65a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n硬碟一顯示未初始化<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08eVXFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08eVXFd.jpg&h=d002d021&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n因為入面有重要既檔同相，所以如果可以救到就盡量救，最起碼可以將裡面既相修復出黎。<br />\n請問怎樣可以救番入面既檔?<br />\n如果不能自救要拿出去整，大概幾錢到?"},{"pid":"a1e538b88feff136015d505b4a4efaba48c93765","tid":1175204,"uid":151540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比個救DATA 收費你參考下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.logicdatarecovery.com/price.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.logicdatarecovery.com%2Fprice.html&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=a4780235\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.logicdatarecovery.com/price.html</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔離post見到"},{"pid":"ca591f8b33d7cf52ddf677fccffcd5b1712d4217","tid":1175204,"uid":133689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1e538b88feff136015d505b4a4efaba48c93765","tid":1175204,"uid":151540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比個救DATA 收費你參考下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.logicdatarecovery.com/price.html\" data-s